'''Sṳ-va̍k''' (字畫) he chṳ́ siá [[hon-sṳ]] ke sṳ̀-heu, m̀ kiên-ton ke yit pit siá sṳ̀n ke yit thiàu sien. Sṳ-va̍k ya-he hon-sṳ chui séu ke keu-sṳ̀n tân-vi.

Chui kî-chhṳ́ ke sṳ-va̍k yû 8 chak: vàng (橫, [[file:Cjk m str h.svg|16px]]), chhṳ̍t (直, [[file:Cjk m str v.svg|16px]]), phiet (撇, [[file:Cjk m str t.svg|16px]]), na̍k (捺, [[file:Cjk m str p.svg|16px]]), tiám (點, [[file:Cjk m str d.svg|16px]]), thiâu (挑, [[file:Cjk m str u.svg|16px]]), kiêu (鈎, [[file:Cjk m str j.svg|16px]]) lâu vân (彎, [[file:Cjk m str c.svg|16px]]).

